  "prompt": "What is the salary for an Android developer with 4+ years experience in Dublin, Ireland?",
  "response": "Salaries can vary widely depending on the industry, company, and individual qualifications. As of 2023, an Android developer with 4+ years of experience in Dublin, Ireland, typically earns between \u20ac50,000 to \u20ac75,000 per year. However, top companies and particularly skilled developers can potentially command higher salaries, sometimes exceeding \u20ac80,000. Additionally, benefits, bonuses, and stock options can significantly augment the total compensation package. It's recommended to check current job listings, company profiles, and salary surveys for the most accurate and up-to-date information.",
